/-!
# Graph factors generated by canonical base letters

A selected set of canonical base letters determines an exact subgraph of the
host graph. This module supplies only that graph-side construction and its
finite-carrier and selected-edge interfaces; it does not assert an expansion
isomorphism for a sequence-lift fibre.
